{"type": "article", "id": 27663, "title": "木塞边桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-02T07:27:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125701kt3NL7loAeh9yzfF.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>小小的软木塞经过设计后也可以成为一件讨喜的家具，比如这款由英国设计师 Jasper Morrison 与瑞士家居品牌 Vitra 合作推出的边桌。它就好像一个软木塞的放大版，而且真的是采用回收来的软木塞制成，质地轻巧方便移动。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.dwr.com/living-ottomans-benches-stools/vitra-cork-stool-c/7826.html\">购买链接</a>，售价为 490 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125659rsLGEP6Z18KwVioj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.30537975\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125700nod7pJg6kfRZBmLF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}